Author: GFC E-AUCTIONS
Title: Starting February 2018, GFC E-AUCTIONS TOKEN launch!
Body: E-Auctioning the Olive Oil & Fruit and Vegetables Greek market.  ICO (ITO:Initial Token Offer) for the development and implementation of Next Generation E-AUCTION infrastructure in Greece for Fruits & Vegetables and Olive Oil, and sync with a Commodity Exchange market for FUTURES contracts based on cryptocurrency as well. In order to implement GFC E-AUCTION platform, we are offering the chance to buy GFC TOKENS (GFC). GFC TOKEN is listed and trading on Ethen DEX market exchange.  For more information: ico@greekfoodcorridors.com        portal: www.greekfoodcorridors.com      The GFC Team

Author: GFC E-AUCTIONS
Title: Starting February 2018, GFC E-AUCTIONS TOKEN launch!
Body: Hi - project is still going on till raising minimum funds for implementation & operation. GFC gives a real solution to a real problem, bringing supply & demand together, through a cloud base e-auction system, at the benefit of all market stakeholders. The cloud base e-auction clock is an instrument which will find the correct market price; a price discovery mechanism based on actual demand (Price on the trading board sets a Reference Price and a limit up & a limit down P).This Agri-commodity marketing channel is new in Greece & the Balkans and can change a lot when operational

Author: GFC E-AUCTIONS
Title: Starting February 2018, GFC E-AUCTIONS TOKEN launch!
Body: Hi- GFC platform is not operational yet. GFC effort to raise necessary funds through ICO is still going on. When operational, it will be profitable as there is no other ICO offering a cloud base e-auction platform for Agri-commodities, networked between the production and consumption sites, as well as between Countries (A coud base e-auction NTW between Athens-Scopje -Serbia- Romania and Bruges/Belgium, our Terminal I). Nor any commodity exchange offering Futures contracts for the underlying commodity of Olive Oil has been working yet, especialy using cryptocurrency.
